Package net.objectzoo.ebc.impl

Class StartBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.objectzoo.ebc.impl.StartBoard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanStart
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StartAndResultBoard, StartAndSignalBoard, StartBase
    public abstract class StartBoard
extends java.lang.Object
implements CanStart
    A base class for a board that CanStart. The implementation contains the boilerplate code required to implement the interface and provides an Event0Delegate for action invocations.
    Author:
    tilmann
